headline: Are You a Momentum Investor? This 1 Stock Could Be the Perfect Pick
summary: The Zacks Style Scores offers investors a way to easily find top-rated stocks based on their investing style. Here's why you should take advantage.

headline: Trump Tariffs Get Personal for the Harris Tweed Makers of the Hebrides
summary: (Bloomberg) -- In December 1957, Reverend Murdoch MacRae traveled from his parish on Lewis and Harris, one of the Outer Hebridean islands off the north west of mainland Scotland, across the Atlantic Ocean to confront the US Federal Trade Commission in Washington. President Dwight D. Eisenhower’s tariffs on woolen imports were threatening an exodus of the island’s workers whose hand-woven tweed jackets, trousers and caps — beloved by Americans from Wall Street bankers to the Kennedys and Hollywoo
